<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
  @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Calibri', 'Arial', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11pt;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: #111111;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.2in 0.5in 0.2in 0.5in;
    max-width: 8.27in;
  }
  h1, h2, h3, p, ul, li, strong, a {
    font-family: 'Calibri', sans-serif;
    color: #111111;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    clear: both;
  }
  a { color: #111111; display: inline-block; width: auto; clear: none; }
  strong { display: inline; width: auto; clear: none; }
  li { display: list-item; width: auto; clear: none; }
  h1 {
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  h2 {
    margin: 15px 0 6px 0;
    font-size: 13pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid #111111;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }
  h3 {
    margin: 10px 0 2px 0;
    font-size: 11pt;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  p {
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    text-align: justify;
  }
  ul {
    margin: 0 0 10px 18px;
    padding: 0;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }
  li {
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    text-align: justify;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 5px;">
            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24pt; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: 'Calibri', sans-serif;">Name</h1>
            <div style="margin-top: 2px; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; color: #333;">AWS Cloud Engineer</div>
            <div style="margin-top: 4px; font-size: 10pt; color: #555;">Hyderabad, India | <a href="">Portfolio</a></div>
            <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1.5px solid #111; margin: 10px 0 12px 0;">
        </div>
        
    <h2 style="text-align: left; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #111;">PROFESSIONAL SUMMARY</h2>
<p>Results-driven General with deep expertise in the tools extracted from the master resume. Committed to high-precision software delivery and technical excellence.</p>

<h2 style="text-align: left; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #111;">EDUCATION</h2>
<p>No education details available.</p>

<h2 style="text-align: left; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #111;">TECHNICAL SKILLS</h2>
<p>No technical skills available.</p>

<h2 style="text-align: left; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #111;">EXPERIENCE</h2>
<p>No experience details available.</p>

<h2 style="text-align: left; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #111;">PROJECTS</h2>
<p>No projects available.</p>

However, since the JSON data does not contain any actual skills, experience, or projects, the above HTML will be generated. If you provide the actual JSON data with the required information, I can generate the HTML accordingly.

Here's an example of how the HTML would look like with some sample data:

{
  "full_name": "John Doe",
  "role_title": "AWS Cloud Engineer",
  "location": "Hyderabad, India",
  "contact": " | ",
  "links": [
    "",
    ""
  ],
  "summary": "Results-driven General with deep expertise in the tools extracted from the master resume. Committed to high-precision software delivery and technical excellence.",
  "education": [],
  "skills": {
    "Programming Languages": ["Python", "Java"],
    "Web Technologies": ["React", "HTML", "CSS"],
    "Backend": ["Node.js", "Django", "Spring Boot"],
    "Database": ["MySQL", "MongoDB", "PostgreSQL"],
    "Tools & Technologies": ["Git", "Docker", "AWS"]
  },
  "experience": [
    {
      "title": "Software Engineer",
      "company": "ABC Corporation",
      "duration": "Jan 2023 - Present"
    }
  ],
  "projects": [
    {
      "name": "Project 1",
      "tech_stack": ["React", "Node.js", "MongoDB"],
      "description": ["Description 1", "Description 2"]
    }
  ]
}

And here's the generated HTML:

<h2 style="text-align: left; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #111;">PROFESSIONAL SUMMARY</h2>
<p>Results-driven General with deep expertise in the tools extracted from the master resume. Committed to high-precision software delivery and technical excellence.</p>

<h2 style="text-align: left; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #111;">EDUCATION</h2>
